    • Method Detail

      • retryLimit

        public RequestBuilderAuthenticate retryLimit(int count)
        Limit for retrying connection if 401 status code is returned and Authentication supports authenticate. Resets Authentication if needed. Default retry limit is 1.
        Parameters:
        count - number of retries
        Returns:
        request builder
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if count is less than zero
        Since:
        SNC 1.0
        See Also:
        Authentication.reset(), Authentication.authenticateSupported()
